articles.title: Australian police probe video of nurses bragging about killing Israelis - Al Jazeera English
articles.description: Prime Minister Anthony Albanese says footage of hospital staff saying they would deny care is ‘sickening and shameful’.
articles.content:
Police in Australia have launched an investigation into a video appearing to show two nurses at a Sydney hospital boasting about killing and denying treatment to Israeli patients.
